id of a price: see 1. ―         -b5-  Said of a camel: see 1. ―         -b6-  Also (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it, went back,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"backward: went away: perished."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b7-  See also R. Q. 1."}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}